.top
You now need to choose a password to restrict access to the account
'sysadm', for system administration.

You will be asked to enter the password after this screen.  The text of the
password as you type it will not appear on the screen.  You will then be
prompted to type the same password again.  See the help facility or the
installation guide for more information.
